another quarter with double-digit growth across its topline primarily due to continued healthy demand for the company's</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1607093280/image_1607093280.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743109-argan-is-still-a-decent-buy-after-q3fy25-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 23:40:25"}, {"id": "4743107", "title": "Autodesk: Stretched Valuation And Fading Tailwinds Will Continue To Create Problems", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"3D product visualization\" data-id=\"156351999\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4500px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/156351999/image_156351999.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">adventtr</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"